Discovered a whole new side of Ibiza from our stay at @7PinesIbiza. From the magic of Es Vedrà & unimaginable sunsets in the west, to the iconic old town in the south & the awe-striking and serene coast in the north, the destination has something for everyone.

📍 @7Pinesibiza @Hyatt @Destinationhotels
📸 @matiasderada + @lizzymcole
🎶 @kasbomusic

Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico
@roth.azulik @byroth_ 
📽 Shot by: @loganstrongarms @cshep @reme_martyr 
🧘🏽‍♀️ @lizzymcole @travelwithadrien @reepetite @emchenyoga @zoejanemitchell @tomjauncey @julianmjung @racheltudoryoga

node.text:
With its Andalusian architecture and Mediterranean elegance, Finca Cortesin gives you an experience of overall luxury you can't forget.✨ You might never want to leave once you stay in their spacious rooms, strolled at their manicured gardens, had a round of golf at their exclusive golf course, and had a cocktail at their beach club, but that's understandable! 😉

Feel the country club vibe while you swipe to see why Finca Cortesin is a dream destination in Spain. It's not hard to imagine yourself there now. Maybe it's time to book a holiday there? ✈️
 
📍 @fincacortesin, Casares, Spain

Eco-glamping with a little razzle-dazzle with @c_a_b_i_n_s_e_e_k_e_r_s at the Leadwood Safari Company. 🇿🇦 Rustic luxuries are offered by the camp located within the Dinokeng Big 5 Game Reserve with amenities that will make you feel at home. Eager to create a different kind of adventure? Your tent is your starting point to experience what the African wilderness has to offer!

💡 BH Tip: Book a game drive! Ask the staff for daily drive schedules for a unique, outdoor activity! Wildlife photographers and bird enthusiasts, this is highly recommended for your itinerary!

Is glamping a part of your travel experience? Would you stay here? 😎
 
📸 @c_a_b_i_n_s_e_e_k_e_r_s

node.text:
Aesthetic feels brought to you by @admbrs. 😍 Experience Art Nouveau grandeur in Splendid Palas Hotel Istanbul as you walk through their luxuriously designed interiors with rooms facing the city or the Marmara Sea. You'll be left wondering if you traveled back in time during your stay, but that's the charm of this beautiful hotel! 🇹🇷

If you're the type to incorporate a little history in your trips, the hotel itself is full of colorful anecdotes and stories spanning decades. Feel free to ask the staff and connect with the locals about this 111-year old icon! ❤️

Are you a fan of Art Nouveau design and architecture? Would you consider staying here? 😍
 
📸 @admbrs
📍 @splendidpalasbuyukada, Istanbul, Turkey

Relaxing with @bomkanari and @iverp in their modernized fisherman's cabin in Lofoten. 😍 Hattvika Lodge gives you an authentic Lofoten experience with their hillside and seaside cabins. In the mood for adventure? The lodge can arrange various activities for you such as ski trips, a Northern lights safari, and the legendary Lofoten fishing! 🎣

Once you are in Lofoten, take a stroll under the "midnight sun". Empty streets and blue skies at midnight are sure to make you feel like you're in another world!

Have you been to Norway? What was your favorite part of your trip? 😍 

📸 @bomkanari and @iverp

Enjoying the view of grazing zebras with @chelseakauai. 🦓 If you're the type to choose staycations that give you a closer look at animals in their natural state, the Gondwana Game Reserve makes it possible! You get to witness African wildlife outside your window, giving you a deeper appreciation for them.

With conservation efforts at the front and center of the game reserve, guests are not only treated to South African hospitality, but are also given unforgettable lessons about protecting wildlife and vegetation. 🌍

💡 BH Tip: Join the reserve's game drives! Watch endemic wildlife from a distance and see the Big 5: the lion, leopard, elephant, buffalo, and the rhinoceros.

Which among the Big 5 are you more interested in seeing up close? Would you want to visit South Africa? 🇿🇦

📽️ @chelseakauai
📍 @gondwanagr, South Africa
🎶 The Japanese House - Saw You In A Dream

Rediscovering Bali with @explorerssaurus. 🇮🇩 The Kamandalu Resort gives couples a gorgeous backdrop to a special romantic getaway with their infinity pools overlooking lush treetops. It sure looks cozy and luxurious, but there is so much more to do. If you're wondering if there is something else to look forward to apart from some R&R, ask the staff about their leisure offerings! 😎

Have you been to Indonesia? What's the best experience you've had there? 😍

Sunsets like these are paired with margaritas, don't you think? 🍹 At Hotel Casa Las Tortugas, experience barefoot living in one of Mexico's "home away from home". With their sustainable practices, your trip will bring you closer to nature while you create new memories without leaving any carbon footprint.

With cozy rooms facing a gorgeous sea, lounge comfortably in your own outdoor hammock and embrace the beach life, guilt-free. 🌊

💡 BH Tip: If you're the type to just lounge in your room to watch TV the whole day, Hotel Casa Las Tortugas doesn't have them. We recommend trying kiteboarding instead! 😉

Are you a beach bum or a holiday thrill-seeker? What's something you haven't tried doing while on holiday? We'd love to know!

📍 @casalastortugas, Holbox, Mexico
🎶 Sumeru - islandman
